nstab-draft: Tab label for pages in the Draft namespace (ID 300).
nstab-draft_talk: Tab label for pages in the Draft talk namespace (ID 301). Not always used; talk tabs often use a generic system message.
nstab-fanmade: Tab label for pages in the Fanmade namespace (ID 302).
nstab-fanmade_talk: Tab label for pages in the Fanmade talk namespace (ID 303). Not always used; talk tabs often use a generic system message.
namespace-draft: Localized name of the Draft namespace (ID 300).
namespace-draft-talk: Localized name of the Draft talk namespace (ID 301).
namespace-fanmade: Localized name of the Fanmade namespace (ID 302).
namespace-fanmade-talk: Localized name of the Fanmade talk namespace (ID 303).
tooltip-ca-nstab-draft: Tooltip for the content tab when viewing a page in the Draft namespace.
tooltip-ca-nstab-fanmade: Tooltip for the content tab when viewing a page in the Fanmade namespace.
tooltip-ca-talk-draft: Tooltip for the talk tab of pages in the Draft namespace.
tooltip-ca-talk-fanmade: Tooltip for the talk tab of pages in the Fanmade namespace.
namespaceinfo-description-ns300: Description shown in namespace information for namespace ID 300 (Draft).
namespaceinfo-description-ns301: Description shown in namespace information for namespace ID 301 (Draft talk).
namespaceinfo-description-ns302: Description shown in namespace information for namespace ID 302 (Fanmade).
namespaceinfo-description-ns303: Description shown in namespace information for namespace ID 303 (Fanmade talk).
